  Delta V^Pauli Coulomb:                -0.526259788749410        -14.3203          -330.23         -1381.69
  Delta V^Pauli LDA-XC:                 -0.210685214224107         -5.7330          -132.21          -553.15
  Delta V^Pauli GGA-Exchange:            0.057905072435830          1.5757            36.34           152.03
  Delta V^Pauli GGA-Correlation:        -0.032602400122149         -0.8872           -20.46           -85.60
                                      --------------------     -----------       ----------      -----------
  Total Pauli Repulsion:                 0.182034316320315          4.9534           114.23           477.93
 (Total Pauli Repulsion =
  Delta E^Pauli in BB paper)

